      "content": "but they're so young. they shouldn't have to see this. they should have a parent who is actually stable and happy, not someone who just makes everything harder. honestly, it feels more selfish to keep dragging them through my darkness than to just stop being a problem for them. it feels like the only way to actually give them a chance at a good life is to just... not be in the way anymore.",
